C - malloc, free

This project introduces dynamic memory allocation in C using malloc and free.

Learning Objectives

At the end of this project, I should be able to explain:

* The difference between automatic and dynamic memory allocation
* What malloc is and how to use it
* What free is and how to use it
* Why and when dynamic memory allocation is needed
* How to use Valgrind to check for memory leaks

